The Crosspays Team    Crosspays is the world's first concept of a self-regulating multinational economic and social system, based on the Idea of Economic Justice and Mutual Benefits.  Crosspays, through Blokchain and the new economic model, absorbs 90% of the revenues of the largest corporations and automatically redistributes them to the income of ordinary people.  The essence of Crosspays is simple: the system aggregates all the main markets for goods and services, which allow Manufacturers of goods and services not to pay huge extra charges to intermediaries and speculators. And simple Users automatically receive income from their actions not only in the Crosspays Community, but also on the Internet. If now, any actions of the User in the Internet are monetized (without his knowledge) only by Monopolies and Internet giants, then Crosspays redistribute this revenue in the User's direction in various ways with the help of Blockchain.  In fact, Crosspays affecting all spheres of economic activity, throws an archaic economic model to the scrapyard, the basis of which is the predatory percentage of the Mediator and the Speculator. The new Digital Economy should and will have the concept of Economic Justice and the Crosspays Community Benefit concept. This means that any active User becomes a beneficiary of the world economy and will receive a portion of the gross income of the world's economic B2B, C2B, B2C, advertising and media markets controlled by only a few hundred multinational corporations.
